title: Grateful Dead Live at Rainbow Theater on 1981-03-24
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step-> Franklin's Tower, Beat It On Down The Line-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Row Jimmy, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, High Time-> Little Red Rooster, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Shakedown Street, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> He's Gone, Drums*-> The Wheel-> Truckin'-> Wharf Rat-> Around & Around-> Good Lovin', E: Brokedown Palace

*with The Flying Karamazov Brothers

reviews.review_text: - Some nice jams, but Garcia tends to fatfinger a lot of licks on this one. Nice long Shakedown. Not bad overall.
